    "description": "The Encore Burst 200 is an IPX4 rated, high intensity dual lens audience blinder/strobe. It’s powered by two 110W warm white (2700K) CREE COB LEDs. The fixture is constructed with a rugged metal housing and an aluminum extrusion rails system to connect multiple fixtures to create a larger cluster of fixtures in a vertical or horizontal array. The fixture features a Tungsten Mode effect that replicates a halogen-like dimming profile.",
